<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="race-v">race <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /reɪs/    美 /reɪs/  </p>
<p>vi &amp; vt</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(与...) 赛跑；(与...) 竞争：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll race you to the corner.
我和你比赛看谁先跑到拐弯处。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>racing /'reɪsɪŋ/    </p></div>